If you use or extend ASaiM framework in your published work, please cite the following publications:

- Bérénice Batut et al. (2016). ASaiM framework: an open-source Galaxy-based opinionated framework dedicated to microbiota sequence analyses. Zenodo. [10.5281/zenodo.56282](https://zenodo.org/record/56282)

